node.text:
Bears hunting for lunch in Alaska 🐻 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on nomadfervor.com (link in my bio: @nomadfervor)

If you’re looking for an epic wildlife experience, Alaska might just be the place for you to visit next. Known and loved for its diverse wildlife, Alaska is home to many species including grizzlies and black bears, wolfs, reindeers, dall sheep and bisons. Would you visit Alaska? 🐺🦌

📽 @mikewolfel
📍 Katmai National Park and Preserve, Alaska, USA
🎶 toastool - Forever (Slowed & Reverb)

node.text:
The beauty of the Faroe Islands 🤍 We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @nomadfervor and we will select your pictures

The Faroe Islands are made up of 18 islands located about 200 miles north-northwest of Scotland and about halfway between Norway & Iceland.  The islands are rugged and rocky with some low peaks; the coasts are mostly cliffs. 

Do you think you'd be interested in visiting? 🇫🇴 

Photos & videos by:
1. @dope4travel 
2. @golden_heart 
3. @patheight 
4. @luigichiurchi 
5. @patheight
